---
import Image from "./Image.astro";
---

<section>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl md:px-12 flex flex-col items-center pt-24 md:pt-36 text-center p-2">
    
  </div>
</section>

<div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4 max-w-[85rem] w-full mx-auto px-6">
  <div class="w-1/2">
    <h1 class="inline-block md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold lowercase">
      hi, i'm tom
      <div class="h-2 w-full bg-orange-500"></div>
      <div class="h-2 w-full bg-pink-600"></div>
      <div class="h-2 w-full bg-purple-400"></div>
    </h1>
    <p>i'm a <strong>front-end developer</strong> and <strong>digital project manager</strong>.</p>
    <p>I learned to make websites on my own. I know how fun and rewarding it is, but I also know that it can be incredibly frustrating. I'm here to help make your journey into web development as easy and as fun as possible.</p>
    <a href="/" class="duration-200 ease-out transition inline-block text-lg text-lg font-bold group hover:-rotate-2 inline-block px-5 py-3 relative rounded-sm text-bold text-shadow block mx-auto text-center" target="_self" rel="" data-astro-cid-vnzlvqnm=""><span class="w-full h-full absolute inset-0 duration-200 ease-out group-hover:-translate-x-0 group-hover:-translate-y-0 transform transition translate-x-1 translate-y-1 bg-primary-blue" data-astro-cid-vnzlvqnm=""></span><span class="w-full h-full absolute inset-0 border-2 border-gray-800 group-hover:bg-primary-blue bg-white" data-astro-cid-vnzlvqnm=""></span><span class="relative group-hover:text-white text-black mr-2" data-astro-cid-vnzlvqnm="">Find out more</span><span class="relative group-hover:text-white text-black fa-chevron-circle-right fa-solid z-10" data-astro-cid-vnzlvqnm=""></span></a>
  </div>
  <div class="w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
    <Image />
  </div>
</div>

<style>

  h1 {
    @apply mb-6;
  }

  p {
    @apply lg:text-2xl mb-6;
  }
</style>
